'''Subrail Park''' is a stadium in [[Labasa]] (pronounced "lum-ba-sa") on the island of [[Vanua Levu]] in [[Fiji]]. The stadium owned and managed by Labasa Town Council. The stadium has a capacity of 10,000 people at any event. It is the home for [[Labasa FC]] and [[Dreketi F.C.|Dreketi]]. It also hosts rugby union matches, such as the [[Colonial Cup (Rugby Union)|Colonial Cup]] and the [[Digicel Cup (Rugby)|Digicel Cup]].

